  "name": "RPlog_Death_of_an_Imperial",
  "title": "The Death of an Imperial",
  "summary": "During the Imperial assault on Coruscant, the aging Grand Admiral Danik Kreldin leads War Shrike Squadron in his signature crimson TIE Interceptor Black Star I, haunted by dark-side voices and a premonition of death as bombers press toward the NRSD Monarch. The New Republic scrambles a massive starfighter response led by Kyrin 'Phoenix' Sh'vani in Ghost 4, joined by the rookie Blake 'Falcon 8' Hishiko, the veteran Kesander 'Sandman' Beysarus, and Captain Lynae Caiton commanding the Broadsword and her escorts. As Kreldin's already-damaged fighter loses control, Kyrin closes in and, despite the protective efforts of Krieg's War Shrikes, Commander Wolf, and the loyal Lanil Jast, batters Black Star I until it erupts in a final explosion, killing the legendary Kreldin. The stunned, enraged Imperials fight on while the New Republic, having achieved their kill and saved the Monarch, withdraw; Caiton solemnly recovers the Admiral's remains for burial as both sides honor the fallen warhorse.",
